metadata.name: Psychedelic Penguin #1
metadata.description: **Mint a collectible psychedelic penguin for only .08 ETH each: https://psychedelicpenguins.com.**  ***Minting is live now!***  *Exclusive offering: Inspired AI-generated Pudgy Penguin artwork*.  Pudgy Penguins is high on the list of the most valuable NFT collections.  Rare Penguins command hundreds of thousands of dollars, and even “floor” Penguins fetch tens of thousands.  For many, this prevents ownership of an original Pudgy Penguin NFT.  Now, through this limited offering, you can mint your own spectacular AI-generated modern artwork based on the full Pudgy Penguin collection.  Employing over 100 AI technologies, this peerless collection takes the Penguins to another level.  New collectors and connoisseurs alike will see the Penguins like never before, with more vibrant colors, lighting effects, and gorgeous detail.  Only one minting is available for each of the 8,888 Pudgy Penguins, with every owner receiving an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain.  Get these collectibles while you still can.
